{"tid":144181,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[求教]如何有效地沖走大量白飯","createTime":"2017-03-05T08:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T04:11:48.000Z","uid":20943,"like":11,"dislike":160,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c7808bdad7056d978099f798f1aba1f69956f8be","tid":144181,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:24:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n今天發現一群穀牛騎劫了小弟一向潔淨的米缸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打擊了小弟一向只想吃一頓安安穩穩o既飯o既願境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為了讓米缸嘅前景著想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是小弟忍痛將所有米倒掉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知道老豆老母至小教訓一碗飯得來不易，要珍惜每一粒米 <br />\n亦都唔好阻人米路 <br />\n但係我唔想，逼不得已 <br />\n請原諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/v54803IMAG1325c90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fv54803IMAG1325c90.jpg&h=063b4452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過個馬桶承受唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲米沖唔走 <br />\n有咩方法可以搞一搞佢 <br />\n通渠水的話得唔得，定係倒Ｄ熱水令佢軟化較為廉價啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求各位巴絲打賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c2dea936f4dc07ee0659f022a9a1fee70dafc20","tid":144181,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:26:08.000Z","msg":"倒入馬筒，你係得嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9112958043edbc506a4b4a015df973279c796344","tid":144181,"uid":894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:26:11.000Z","msg":"on99<br />\n有垃圾桶唔撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3567a18d3f362f8fc5b957065f089b160114d406","tid":144181,"uid":8534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":